      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Somniferous Elegy",
        "Client": "Inn Keeper",
        "Description": "Had a group of travelers come in\r\nlast night fleeing a Somnacanth.\r\nDang monster must have got \u0027em\r\ngood because they\u0027re still sleepin\u0027!\r\nI can\u0027t have guests stayin\u0027 past\r\ncheck out time! Hunter, can ya\r\ngo do something \u0027bout that thing?",
